title: Humana, UnitedHealth plunge 20% after Trump administration proposes keeping Medicare Advantage rates flat
summary: Shares of large Medicare plan providers Humana, CVS Health and UnitedHealth Group plunged in extended trading.

title: US health insurer shares fall on proposal to cut rise in Medicare payments
